SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM title t, cast_info ci, movie_keyword mk
WHERE t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.kind_id  =  3 AND t.production_year  <  1959 AND mk.keyword_id  >  40242
